ning career fair designed to bring juniors  seniors and recent graduates together with representatives from various companies and agencies  It is an effective way for employers to meet and recruit students from 8 prestigious Virginia colleges universities  UVA JOB AND INTERNSHIP FAIR Students from all colleges and universities across Virginia and Washington  DC are welcome to attend  Last year  more than 150 corporations  government agencies  and non profit organizations participated  Many recruiters have specifically indicated that they like this event because they have the opportunity to meet students from so many different schools  CAREER PREMIERE is another career fair opportunity held each spring for VMI cadets to attend  Eight schools support this fair and have given an open invitation for us to attend  SOUTHERN TEACHERS FAIR  The Southern Teachers Agency STA hosts an annual teacher recruitment fair in Charlottesville so that private school teachers can find the best teaching vacancies  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu Virginia Military Institute   Career Fairs       Virginia Military Institute   Career Fairs                     skip to content VMI VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI Menu About About Us Administrative Offices Institute Report News  Photos  Videos VMI Archives Museums VMI Museum System The VMI Museum New Market Battlefield Stonewall Jackson House For Visitors Di