ar  more than 150 corporations  government agencies  and non profit organizations participated  Many recruiters have specifically indicated that they like this event because they have the opportunity to meet students from so many different schools  CAREER PREMIERE is another career fair opportunity held each spring for VMI cadets to attend  Eight schools support this fair and have given an open invitation for us to attend  SOUTHERN TEACHERS FAIR  The Southern Teachers Agency STA hosts an annual teacher recruitment fair in Charlottesville so that private school teachers can find the best teaching vacancies Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Cadets Cadet Newsletter  Turnout  Alumni Career Vignettes Resume Writing Job Search Self   Assessment Career Research Career Fairs Business Etiquette Graduate School Student Consumer Info Employers Alumni Faculty   Staff Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Mrs Kaye Taylor Office Manager Ph   540  464 7560 Fax   540  464 7367 Career Services Office Virginia Military Institute 311 Carroll Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Contact Career Services  Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Cadets Cadet Newsletter  Turnout  Alumni Career Vignettes Resume Writing Job Search Self   Assessment Career Research Career Fairs Business Etiquette Graduate School Student Consumer Info Employers Alumni Faculty   Staff Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Mrs Kaye Taylor Office Manager Ph   540  464 7560 Fax   540  464 7367 Career Services Office Virginia Military Institute 311 Carroll Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Contact Career Services Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Cadets Cadet Newsletter  Turnout  Alumni Career Vignettes Resume Writing Job Search Self   Assessment Career Research Career Fairs Business Etiquette Graduate School Student Consumer Info Employers Alumni Faculty   Staff Family   Visitors Career Services Staff Academic Services   Support Academic Services   Support Career Services Home Career Services