es  UVA JOB AND INTERNSHIP FAIR Students from all colleges and universities across Virginia and Washington  DC are welcome to attend  Last year  more than 150 corporations  government agencies  and non profit organizations participated  Many recruiters have specifically indicated that they like this event because they have the opportunity to meet students from so many different schools  CAREER PREMIERE is another career fair opportunity held each spring for VMI cadets to attend  Eight schools support this fair and have given an open invitation for us to attend  SOUTHERN TEACHERS FAIR  The Southern Teachers Agency STA hosts an annual teacher recruitment fair in Charlottesville so that private school teachers can find the best teaching vacancies      Career Fairs Career Fairs provide excellent opportunities to meet with employers who advertise job and internship opportunities each year  It allows cadets to meet with employers and recruiters face to face and ask questions about opportunities  Below are a number of annual Career Fairs that could be helpful in your job or internship searching  CHALLENGE is a job fair held each year in the fall  CHALLENGE is an award winning career fair designed to bring juniors  seniors and recent graduates together with representatives from various companies and agencies  It is an effective way for employers to meet and recruit students from 8 prestigious Virginia colleges universities  UVA JOB AND INTERNSHIP FAIR Students from all colleges and universities across Virginia and Washington  DC are welcome to attend  Last year  more than 150 corporations  government agencies  and non profit organizations participated  Many recruiters have specifically indicated that they like this event because they have the opportunity to meet students from so many different schools  CAREER PREMIERE is another career fair opportunity held each spring for VMI cadets to attend  Eight schools support this fair and have given an open invitation for us to atte